Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.validator

Class UiTableValidatorImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.validator.UiTableValidatorImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
UiTableValidator
public class UiTableValidatorImpl extends Object implements UiTableValidator
Implementation of UiTableValidator responsible for validating table data and elements.

This class provides methods for extracting table row values, table elements, and performing assertions on tables based on different validation targets.

    • validateTable

      public <T> List<io.cyborgcode.roa.validator.core.AssertionResult<T>> validateTable(Object object, io.cyborgcode.roa.validator.core.Assertion... assertions)
      Validates the given table object against a set of assertions.

      Extracts data based on the assertion target (row values, row elements, table values, or table elements), logs the validation target, and executes assertions on the extracted data.

      Specified by:
      validateTable in interface UiTableValidator
      Type Parameters:
      T - The expected type of assertion results.
      Parameters:
      object - The table object to validate.
      assertions - The assertions to apply.
      Returns:
      A list of assertion results indicating whether the validation passed or failed.

    • startValidation

      public void startValidation(int assertionCount)
